headline: Why The Trade Desk (TTD) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of advertising software maker The Trade Desk (NASDAQ:TTD) jumped 3.7% in the afternoon session after an analyst at BTIG reaffirmed a 'Buy' rating and raised the price target on the stock.

headline: 1 Unpopular Stock That Should Get More Attention and 2 We Question
summary: When Wall Street turns bearish on a stock, it’s worth paying attention. These calls stand out because analysts rarely issue grim ratings on companies for fear their firms will lose out in other business lines such as M&A advisory.
